    <section id="id4854320">
      <title>NATIONAL FESTIVE DAYS AND THE SOUTH AFRICAN ANTHEM</title>
      <para id="id10472199">National festive days in South Africa</para>
      <para id="id4865062">We celebrate a number of festive days in South Africa. Think of Workers Day (1 May), Youth Day (16 June) and National Heritage Day (24 September).</para>
      <section id="id6492788">
