      <section id="id4609964">
        <title>[LO 2.5]</title>
        <para id="id4827558">Do you know the words of our national anthem? Write out the words as attractively as you can on a sheet of paper and decorate its edges with a colourful pattern. It may be a good idea to use the colours of our national flag.</para>
        <para id="id4865458">Plan a special Heritage Day celebration for your school. Who would you invite as guests? Which songs would you sing at assembly? Which special person in South Africa would you like to honour on Heritage Day?</para>
      </section>
